description: A React component for managing Jira projects, including searching and creating projects via API calls.

methods.name: search
methods.description: Asynchronous function to search Jira projects using provided tenant and connector IDs, updating the result or error state.

methods.name: create
methods.description: Asynchronous function to create a new Jira project with specified tenant, connector, and query name, updating the result or error state.
